request.description:
### Delete Address Alteration Policy API

**HTTP Request:**

- Method: POST

- URL: `https://api.services.mimecast.com/api/policy/address-alteration/delete-policy`

- Content-Type: application/json


**Request Body (required):**

- Structure: JSON object with a "data" array containing from 1 to 500 items.

- Each item in the "data" array must have:

    - "id" (required): The Mimecast secure id of the policy to be deleted.


**Example Request Body:**

``` json
{
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "fake_policy_id_123"  # Replace with the actual Mimecast secure id of the Address Alteration Policy you want to delete.
    },
    {
      "id": "fake_policy_id_456"  # Another example policy id (replace with real id if needed).
    }
  ]
}

 ```

